37struct dns_lookup {
38 /* Unlocked. */
39 unsigned int magic;
40 isc_mem_t * mctx;
41 isc_mutex_t lock;
42 dns_rdatatype_t type;
43 dns_fixedname_t name;
44 /* Locked by lock. */
45 unsigned int options;
46 isc_task_t * task;
47 dns_view_t * view;
48 dns_lookupevent_t * event;
49 dns_fetch_t * fetch;
50 unsigned int restarts;
51 bool canceled;
52 dns_rdataset_t rdataset;
53 dns_rdataset_t sigrdataset;
54};
55
56#define LOOKUP_MAGIC ISC_MAGIC('l', 'o', 'o', 'k')
57#define VALID_LOOKUP(l) ISC_MAGIC_VALID((l), LOOKUP_MAGIC)
58
59#define MAX_RESTARTS 16
60
61static void lookup_find(dns_lookup_t *lookup, dns_fetchevent_t *event);
62
63static void
64fetch_done(isc_task_t *task, isc_event_t *event) {
65 dns_lookup_t *lookup = event->ev_arg;
66 dns_fetchevent_t *fevent;
67
68 UNUSED(task);
69 REQUIRE(event->ev_type == DNS_EVENT_FETCHDONE);
70 REQUIRE(VALID_LOOKUP(lookup));
71 REQUIRE(lookup->task == task);
72 fevent = (dns_fetchevent_t *)event;
73 REQUIRE(fevent->fetch == lookup->fetch);
74
75 lookup_find(lookup, fevent);
76}
77
78static inline isc_result_t
79start_fetch(dns_lookup_t *lookup) {
80 isc_result_t result;
81
82 /*
83 * The caller must be holding the lookup's lock.
84 */
85
86 REQUIRE(lookup->fetch == NULL);
87
88 result = dns_resolver_createfetch(lookup->view->resolver,
89 dns_fixedname_name(&lookup->name),
90 lookup->type,
91 NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0,
92 NULL,
93 lookup->task, fetch_done, lookup,
94 &lookup->rdataset,
95 &lookup->sigrdataset,
96 &lookup->fetch);
97
98 return (result);
99}
100
101static isc_result_t
102build_event(dns_lookup_t *lookup) {
103 dns_name_t *name = NULL;
104 dns_rdataset_t *rdataset = NULL;
105 dns_rdataset_t *sigrdataset = NULL;
106 isc_result_t result;
107
108 name = isc_mem_get(lookup->mctx, sizeof(dns_name_t));
109 if (name == NULL) {
110 result = ISC_R_NOMEMORY;
111 goto fail;
112 }
113 dns_name_init(name, NULL);
114 result = dns_name_dup(dns_fixedname_name(&lookup->name),
115 lookup->mctx, name);
116 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
117 goto fail;
118
119 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&lookup->rdataset)) {
120 rdataset = isc_mem_get(lookup->mctx, sizeof(dns_rdataset_t));
121 if (rdataset == NULL) {
122 result = ISC_R_NOMEMORY;
123 goto fail;
124 }
125 dns_rdataset_init(rdataset);
126 dns_rdataset_clone(&lookup->rdataset, rdataset);
127 }
128
129 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&lookup->sigrdataset)) {
130 sigrdataset = isc_mem_get(lookup->mctx,
131 sizeof(dns_rdataset_t));
132 if (sigrdataset == NULL) {
133 result = ISC_R_NOMEMORY;
134 goto fail;
135 }
136 dns_rdataset_init(sigrdataset);
137 dns_rdataset_clone(&lookup->sigrdataset, sigrdataset);
138 }
139
140 lookup->event->name = name;
141 lookup->event->rdataset = rdataset;
142 lookup->event->sigrdataset = sigrdataset;
143
144 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
145
146 fail:
147 if (name != NULL) {
148 if (dns_name_dynamic(name))
149 dns_name_free(name, lookup->mctx);
150 isc_mem_put(lookup->mctx, name, sizeof(dns_name_t));
151 }
152 if (rdataset != NULL) {
153 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(rdataset))
154 dns_rdataset_disassociate(rdataset);
155 isc_mem_put(lookup->mctx, rdataset, sizeof(dns_rdataset_t));
156 }
157 return (result);
158}
159
160static isc_result_t
161view_find(dns_lookup_t *lookup, dns_name_t *foundname) {
162 isc_result_t result;
163 dns_name_t *name = dns_fixedname_name(&lookup->name);
164 dns_rdatatype_t type;
165
166 if (lookup->type == dns_rdatatype_rrsig)
167 type = dns_rdatatype_any;
168 else
169 type = lookup->type;
170
171 result = dns_view_find(lookup->view, name, type, 0, 0, false,
172 false, &lookup->event->db,
173 &lookup->event->node, foundname,
174 &lookup->rdataset, &lookup->sigrdataset);
175 return (result);
176}
177
178static void
179lookup_find(dns_lookup_t *lookup, dns_fetchevent_t *event) {
180 isc_result_t result;
181 bool want_restart;
182 bool send_event;
183 dns_name_t *name, *fname, *prefix;
184 dns_fixedname_t foundname, fixed;
185 dns_rdata_t rdata = DNS_RDATA_INIT;
186 unsigned int nlabels;
187 int order;
188 dns_namereln_t namereln;
189 dns_rdata_cname_t cname;
190 dns_rdata_dname_t dname;
191
192 REQUIRE(VALID_LOOKUP(lookup));
193
194 LOCK(&lookup->lock);
195
196 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
197 name = dns_fixedname_name(&lookup->name);
198
199 do {
200 lookup->restarts++;
201 want_restart = false;
202 send_event = true;
203
204 if (event == NULL && !lookup->canceled) {
205 fname = dns_fixedname_initname(&foundname);
206 INSIST(!dns_rdataset_isassociated(&lookup->rdataset));
207 INSIST(!dns_rdataset_isassociated
208 (&lookup->sigrdataset));
209 /*
210 * If we have restarted then clear the old node. */
211 if (lookup->event->node != NULL) {
212 INSIST(lookup->event->db != NULL);
213 dns_db_detachnode(lookup->event->db,
214 &lookup->event->node);
215 }
216 if (lookup->event->db != NULL)
217 dns_db_detach(&lookup->event->db);
218 result = view_find(lookup, fname);
219 if (result == ISC_R_NOTFOUND) {
220 /*
221 * We don't know anything about the name.
222 * Launch a fetch.
223 */
224 if (lookup->event->node != NULL) {
225 INSIST(lookup->event->db != NULL);
226 dns_db_detachnode(lookup->event->db,
227 &lookup->event->node);
228 }
229 if (lookup->event->db != NULL)
230 dns_db_detach(&lookup->event->db);
231 result = start_fetch(lookup);
232 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS)
233 send_event = false;
234 goto done;
235 }
236 } else if (event != NULL) {
237 result = event->result;
238 fname = dns_fixedname_name(&event->foundname);
239 dns_resolver_destroyfetch(&lookup->fetch);
240 INSIST(event->rdataset == &lookup->rdataset);
241 INSIST(event->sigrdataset == &lookup->sigrdataset);
242 } else
243 fname = NULL; /* Silence compiler warning. */
244
245 /*
246 * If we've been canceled, forget about the result.
247 */
248 if (lookup->canceled)
249 result = ISC_R_CANCELED;
250
251 switch (result) {
252 case ISC_R_SUCCESS:
253 result = build_event(lookup);
254 if (event == NULL)
255 break;
256 if (event->db != NULL)
257 dns_db_attach(event->db, &lookup->event->db);
258 if (event->node != NULL)
259 dns_db_attachnode(lookup->event->db,
260 event->node,
261 &lookup->event->node);
262 break;
263 case DNS_R_CNAME:
264 /*
265 * Copy the CNAME's target into the lookup's
266 * query name and start over.
267 */
268 result = dns_rdataset_first(&lookup->rdataset);
269 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
270 break;
271 dns_rdataset_current(&lookup->rdataset, &rdata);
272 result = dns_rdata_tostruct(&rdata, &cname, NULL);
273 dns_rdata_reset(&rdata);
274 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
275 break;
276 result = dns_name_copy(&cname.cname, name, NULL);
277 dns_rdata_freestruct(&cname);
278 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
279 want_restart = true;
280 send_event = false;
281 }
282 break;
283 case DNS_R_DNAME:
284 namereln = dns_name_fullcompare(name, fname, &order,
285 &nlabels);
286 INSIST(namereln == dns_namereln_subdomain);
287 /*
288 * Get the target name of the DNAME.
289 */
290 result = dns_rdataset_first(&lookup->rdataset);
291 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
292 break;
293 dns_rdataset_current(&lookup->rdataset, &rdata);
294 result = dns_rdata_tostruct(&rdata, &dname, NULL);
295 dns_rdata_reset(&rdata);
296 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
297 break;
298 /*
299 * Construct the new query name and start over.
300 */
301 prefix = dns_fixedname_initname(&fixed);
302 dns_name_split(name, nlabels, prefix, NULL);
303 result = dns_name_concatenate(prefix, &dname.dname,
304 name, NULL);
305 dns_rdata_freestruct(&dname);
306 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
307 want_restart = true;
308 send_event = false;
309 }
310 break;
311 default:
312 send_event = true;
313 }
314
315 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&lookup->rdataset))
316 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&lookup->rdataset);
317 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&lookup->sigrdataset))
318 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&lookup->sigrdataset);
319
320 done:
321 if (event != NULL) {
322 if (event->node != NULL)
323 dns_db_detachnode(event->db, &event->node);
324 if (event->db != NULL)
325 dns_db_detach(&event->db);
326 isc_event_free(ISC_EVENT_PTR(&event));
327 }
328
329 /*
330 * Limit the number of restarts.
331 */
332 if (want_restart && lookup->restarts == MAX_RESTARTS) {
333 want_restart = false;
334 result = ISC_R_QUOTA;
335 send_event = true;
336 }
337
338 } while (want_restart);
339
340 if (send_event) {
341 lookup->event->result = result;
342 lookup->event->ev_sender = lookup;
343 isc_task_sendanddetach(&lookup->task,
344 (isc_event_t **)(void *)&lookup->event);
345 dns_view_detach(&lookup->view);
346 }
347
348 UNLOCK(&lookup->lock);
349}
350
351static void
352levent_destroy(isc_event_t *event) {
353 dns_lookupevent_t *levent;
354 isc_mem_t *mctx;
355
356 REQUIRE(event->ev_type == DNS_EVENT_LOOKUPDONE);
357 mctx = event->ev_destroy_arg;
358 levent = (dns_lookupevent_t *)event;
359
360 if (levent->name != NULL) {
361 if (dns_name_dynamic(levent->name))
362 dns_name_free(levent->name, mctx);
363 isc_mem_put(mctx, levent->name, sizeof(dns_name_t));
364 }
365 if (levent->rdataset != NULL) {
366 dns_rdataset_disassociate(levent->rdataset);
367 isc_mem_put(mctx, levent->rdataset, sizeof(dns_rdataset_t));
368 }
369 if (levent->sigrdataset != NULL) {
370 dns_rdataset_disassociate(levent->sigrdataset);
371 isc_mem_put(mctx, levent->sigrdataset, sizeof(dns_rdataset_t));
372 }
373 if (levent->node != NULL)
374 dns_db_detachnode(levent->db, &levent->node);
375 if (levent->db != NULL)
376 dns_db_detach(&levent->db);
377 isc_mem_put(mctx, event, event->ev_size);
378}
379
380isc_result_t
381dns_lookup_create(isc_mem_t *mctx, const dns_name_t *name, dns_rdatatype_t type,
382 dns_view_t *view, unsigned int options, isc_task_t *task,
383 isc_taskaction_t action, void *arg, dns_lookup_t **lookupp)
384{
385 isc_result_t result;
386 dns_lookup_t *lookup;
387 isc_event_t *ievent;
388
389 lookup = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(*lookup));
390 if (lookup == NULL)
391 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
392 lookup->mctx = NULL;
393 isc_mem_attach(mctx, &lookup->mctx);
394 lookup->options = options;
395
396 ievent = isc_event_allocate(mctx, lookup, DNS_EVENT_LOOKUPDONE,
397 action, arg, sizeof(*lookup->event));
398 if (ievent == NULL) {
399 result = ISC_R_NOMEMORY;
400 goto cleanup_lookup;
401 }
402 lookup->event = (dns_lookupevent_t *)ievent;
403 lookup->event->ev_destroy = levent_destroy;
404 lookup->event->ev_destroy_arg = mctx;
405 lookup->event->result = ISC_R_FAILURE;
406 lookup->event->name = NULL;
407 lookup->event->rdataset = NULL;
408 lookup->event->sigrdataset = NULL;
409 lookup->event->db = NULL;
410 lookup->event->node = NULL;
411
412 lookup->task = NULL;
413 isc_task_attach(task, &lookup->task);
414
415 isc_mutex_init(&lookup->lock);
416
417 dns_fixedname_init(&lookup->name);
418
419 result = dns_name_copy(name, dns_fixedname_name(&lookup->name), NULL);
420 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
421 goto cleanup_lock;
422
423 lookup->type = type;
424 lookup->view = NULL;
425 dns_view_attach(view, &lookup->view);
426 lookup->fetch = NULL;
427 lookup->restarts = 0;
428 lookup->canceled = false;
429 dns_rdataset_init(&lookup->rdataset);
430 dns_rdataset_init(&lookup->sigrdataset);
431 lookup->magic = LOOKUP_MAGIC;
432
433 *lookupp = lookup;
434
435 lookup_find(lookup, NULL);
436
437 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
438
439 cleanup_lock:
440 isc_mutex_destroy(&lookup->lock);
441 ievent = (isc_event_t *)lookup->event;
442 isc_event_free(&ievent);
443 lookup->event = NULL;
444
445 isc_task_detach(&lookup->task);
446
447 cleanup_lookup:
448 isc_mem_putanddetach(&mctx, lookup, sizeof(*lookup));
449
450 return (result);
451}
452
453void
454dns_lookup_cancel(dns_lookup_t *lookup) {
455 REQUIRE(VALID_LOOKUP(lookup));
456
457 LOCK(&lookup->lock);
458
459 if (!lookup->canceled) {
460 lookup->canceled = true;
461 if (lookup->fetch != NULL) {
462 INSIST(lookup->view != NULL);
463 dns_resolver_cancelfetch(lookup->fetch);
464 }
465 }
466
467 UNLOCK(&lookup->lock);
468}
469
470void
471dns_lookup_destroy(dns_lookup_t **lookupp) {
472 dns_lookup_t *lookup;
473
474 REQUIRE(lookupp != NULL);
475 lookup = *lookupp;
476 REQUIRE(VALID_LOOKUP(lookup));
477 REQUIRE(lookup->event == NULL);
478 REQUIRE(lookup->task == NULL);
479 REQUIRE(lookup->view == NULL);
480 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&lookup->rdataset))
481 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&lookup->rdataset);
482 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&lookup->sigrdataset))
483 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&lookup->sigrdataset);
484
485 isc_mutex_destroy(&lookup->lock);
486 lookup->magic = 0;
487 isc_mem_putanddetach(&lookup->mctx, lookup, sizeof(*lookup));
488
489 *lookupp = NULL;
490}
